name: The End of America
description:
Made in 2019, The End of America is a statement to the political climate in the USA and a testament to how quickly even the strongest of democracies can decline into chaos when that country is led by a corrupt and incompetent "leader".

Comprised of capitalist Americana, both literal and stereotypical.

By @dehiscenceart, 2019. 5400px X 7200px
